title: Oh Maya! Moore hits winner to lift Lynx over Fever 80-77
text:
> Sports Oh Maya! Moore hits winner to lift Lynx over Fever 80-77 Minnesota Lynx forward Maya Moore (23) shoots a game winning three-pointer in the second half of Game 3 of the WNBA Finals basketball series against the Indiana Fever, Friday, Oct. 9, 2015, in Indianapolis. Lynx won 80-77. (AP Photo/AJ Mast)
